    <bf:summary>
      <bf:Summary>
	<rdfs:label>A complete text of the 2nd edition of the Oxford English dictionary with quarterly updates, including revisions not available in any other form. Contains the complete text of the 20-volume second edition together with its 3-volume additions series. New words and revised entries are added quarterly. Also includes the Historical Thesaurus of the OED, a taxonomic classification of the majority of senses and lemmas in OED Online.</rdfs:label>
      </bf:Summary>
    </bf:summary>
